Class AsyncTaskCompat<Params,Progress,Result>

java.lang.Object
  com.appglu.android.task.AsyncTaskCompat<Params,Progress,Result>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AppGluAsyncTaskCompat
public abstract class AsyncTaskCompat<Params,Progress,Result>
extends Object

This class was copied from Ice Cream Sandwich to make it possible to execute tasks with a serial thread pool executor on Android versions before HONEYCOMB.
